
You need to install a package/library name pywhatkit      pip install pywhatkit
*
*
import pywhatkit
pywhatkit.sendwhatmsg('country_code + phone_number', 'Message', hours, minutes, wait_time, print_wait_time)
*
*



Example:
import pywhatkit
pywhatkit.sendwhatmsg('+91- XXXXXXXXX03', 'how do they do it', 17,20)

+91-XXXXXXXX03-           contact number
'how do they do it'       message 
17                        hours
20                        minutes

here we have not mentioned the wait_time & print_wait_time  and we use the default time i.e. 20sec for both.

